{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "6.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "古之民未知爲宮室時，就陵阜而居，穴而處。", "text_normalized": "古之民未知爲宮室時，就陵阜而居，穴而處。", "canonical_ref": "6.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "下潤濕傷民，故聖王作爲宮室。", "text_normalized": "下潤濕傷民，故聖王作爲宮室。", "canonical_ref": "6.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "爲宮室之法，曰：", "text_normalized": "爲宮室之法，曰：", "canonical_ref": "6.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "室高足以辟潤濕，邊足以圉風寒，上足以待雪霜雨露，宮牆之高足以別男女之禮。", "text_normalized": "室高足以辟潤濕，邊足以圉風寒，上足以待雪霜雨露，宮牆之高足以別男女之禮。", "canonical_ref": "6.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "謹此則止。", "text_normalized": "謹此則止。", "canonical_ref": "6.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "凡費財勞力，不加利者，不爲也。", "text_normalized": "凡費財勞力，不加利者，不爲也。", "canonical_ref": "6.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "役，脩其城郭，則民勞而不傷；", "text_normalized": "役，脩其城郭，則民勞而不傷；", "canonical_ref": "6.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "以其常正，收其租稅，則民費而不病。", "text_normalized": "以其常正，收其租稅，則民費而不病。", "canonical_ref": "6.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "民所苦者，非此也，苦於厚作斂於百姓。", "text_normalized": "民所苦者，非此也，苦於厚作斂於百姓。", "canonical_ref": "6.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "[1]是故聖王作爲宮室，便於生，不以爲觀樂也。", "text_normalized": "[1]是故聖王作爲宮室，便於生，不以爲觀樂也。", "canonical_ref": "6.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "作爲衣服帶履，便於身，不以爲辟怪也。", "text_normalized": "作爲衣服帶履，便於身，不以爲辟怪也。", "canonical_ref": "6.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "故節於身，誨於民，是以天下之民可得而治，財用可得而足。", "text_normalized": "故節於身，誨於民，是以天下之民可得而治，財用可得而足。", "canonical_ref": "6.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "當今之主，其爲宮室則與此異矣。", "text_normalized": "當今之主，其爲宮室則與此異矣。", "canonical_ref": "6.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "必厚作斂於百姓，暴奪民衣食之財，以爲宮室臺榭曲直之望、青黃刻鏤之飾。", "text_normalized": "必厚作斂於百姓，暴奪民衣食之財，以爲宮室臺榭曲直之望、青黃刻鏤之飾。", "canonical_ref": "6.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "爲宮室若此，故左右皆法象之。", "text_normalized": "爲宮室若此，故左右皆法象之。", "canonical_ref": "6.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "是以其財不足以待凶饑，振孤寡，故國貧而民難治也。", "text_normalized": "是以其財不足以待凶饑，振孤寡，故國貧而民難治也。", "canonical_ref": "6.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂也，當爲宮室不可不節。", "text_normalized": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂也，當爲宮室不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "古之民未知爲衣服時，衣皮帶茭，冬則不輕而溫，夏則不輕而清。", "text_normalized": "古之民未知爲衣服時，衣皮帶茭，冬則不輕而溫，夏則不輕而清。", "canonical_ref": "6.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "聖王以爲不中人之情，故作誨婦人治絲麻，梱布絹，以爲民衣。", "text_normalized": "聖王以爲不中人之情，故作誨婦人治絲麻，梱布絹，以爲民衣。", "canonical_ref": "6.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "爲衣服之法：", "text_normalized": "爲衣服之法：", "canonical_ref": "6.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "冬則練帛之中，足以爲輕且煖；", "text_normalized": "冬則練帛之中，足以爲輕且煖；", "canonical_ref": "6.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "夏則絺綌之中，足以爲輕且凊。", "text_normalized": "夏則絺綌之中，足以爲輕且凊。", "canonical_ref": "6.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "謹此則止。", "text_normalized": "謹此則止。", "canonical_ref": "6.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "故聖人爲衣服，適身體，和肌膚而足矣，非榮耳目而觀愚民也。", "text_normalized": "故聖人爲衣服，適身體，和肌膚而足矣，非榮耳目而觀愚民也。", "canonical_ref": "6.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "當是之時，堅車良馬不知貴也，刻鏤文采不知喜也。", "text_normalized": "當是之時，堅車良馬不知貴也，刻鏤文采不知喜也。", "canonical_ref": "6.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "何則？", "text_normalized": "何則？", "canonical_ref": "6.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "其所道之然。", "text_normalized": "其所道之然。", "canonical_ref": "6.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "故民衣食之財，家足以待旱水凶饑者，何也？", "text_normalized": "故民衣食之財，家足以待旱水凶饑者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "6.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "得其所以自養之情，而不感於外也。", "text_normalized": "得其所以自養之情，而不感於外也。", "canonical_ref": "6.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "是以其民儉而易治，其君用財節而易贍也。", "text_normalized": "是以其民儉而易治，其君用財節而易贍也。", "canonical_ref": "6.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "府庫實滿，足以待不然。", "text_normalized": "府庫實滿，足以待不然。", "canonical_ref": "6.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "兵革不頓，士民不勞，足以征不服。", "text_normalized": "兵革不頓，士民不勞，足以征不服。", "canonical_ref": "6.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "故霸王之業可行於天下矣。", "text_normalized": "故霸王之業可行於天下矣。", "canonical_ref": "6.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "當今之王，其爲衣服，則與此異矣。", "text_normalized": "當今之王，其爲衣服，則與此異矣。", "canonical_ref": "6.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "冬則輕煗，夏則輕凊，皆已具矣，必厚作斂於百姓，暴奪民衣食之財，以爲錦繡文采靡曼之衣，鑄金以爲鉤，珠玉以爲珮，女工作文采，男工作刻鏤，以爲身服。", "text_normalized": "冬則輕煗，夏則輕凊，皆已具矣，必厚作斂於百姓，暴奪民衣食之財，以爲錦繡文采靡曼之衣，鑄金以爲鉤，珠玉以爲珮，女工作文采，男工作刻鏤，以爲身服。", "canonical_ref": "6.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "此非云益煗之情也。", "text_normalized": "此非云益煗之情也。", "canonical_ref": "6.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "單財勞力，畢歸之於無用也。", "text_normalized": "單財勞力，畢歸之於無用也。", "canonical_ref": "6.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "以此觀之，其爲衣服，非爲身體，皆爲觀好。", "text_normalized": "以此觀之，其爲衣服，非爲身體，皆爲觀好。", "canonical_ref": "6.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "是以其民淫僻而難治，其君奢侈而難諫也。", "text_normalized": "是以其民淫僻而難治，其君奢侈而難諫也。", "canonical_ref": "6.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "夫以奢侈之君御好淫僻之民，欲國無亂，不可得也。", "text_normalized": "夫以奢侈之君御好淫僻之民，欲國無亂，不可得也。", "canonical_ref": "6.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂，當爲衣服不可不節。", "text_normalized": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂，當爲衣服不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "古之民未知爲飲食時，素食而分處。", "text_normalized": "古之民未知爲飲食時，素食而分處。", "canonical_ref": "6.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "故聖人作誨男耕稼樹藝，以爲民食。", "text_normalized": "故聖人作誨男耕稼樹藝，以爲民食。", "canonical_ref": "6.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "其爲食也，足以增氣充虛，強體適腹而已矣。", "text_normalized": "其爲食也，足以增氣充虛，強體適腹而已矣。", "canonical_ref": "6.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "故其用財節，其自養儉，民富國治。", "text_normalized": "故其用財節，其自養儉，民富國治。", "canonical_ref": "6.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "今則不然，厚作斂於百姓，以爲美食芻豢，蒸炙魚鼈。", "text_normalized": "今則不然，厚作斂於百姓，以爲美食芻豢，蒸炙魚鼈。", "canonical_ref": "6.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "大國累百器，小國累十器，美食方丈，目不能徧視，手不能徧操，口不能徧味。", "text_normalized": "大國累百器，小國累十器，美食方丈，目不能徧視，手不能徧操，口不能徧味。", "canonical_ref": "6.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "冬則凍冰，夏則飾饐。", "text_normalized": "冬則凍冰，夏則飾饐。", "canonical_ref": "6.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "人君爲飲食如此，故左右象之。", "text_normalized": "人君爲飲食如此，故左右象之。", "canonical_ref": "6.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "是以富貴者奢侈，孤寡者凍餒，雖欲無亂，不可得也。", "text_normalized": "是以富貴者奢侈，孤寡者凍餒，雖欲無亂，不可得也。", "canonical_ref": "6.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "君實欲天下治而惡其亂，當爲食飲不可不節。", "text_normalized": "君實欲天下治而惡其亂，當爲食飲不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "古之民未知爲舟車時，重任不移，遠道不至。", "text_normalized": "古之民未知爲舟車時，重任不移，遠道不至。", "canonical_ref": "6.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "故聖王作爲舟車，以便民之事。", "text_normalized": "故聖王作爲舟車，以便民之事。", "canonical_ref": "6.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "其爲舟車也，全固輕利，可以任重致遠。", "text_normalized": "其爲舟車也，全固輕利，可以任重致遠。", "canonical_ref": "6.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "其爲用財少而爲利多，是以民樂而利之。", "text_normalized": "其爲用財少而爲利多，是以民樂而利之。", "canonical_ref": "6.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "故法令不急而行，民不勞而上足用，故民歸之。", "text_normalized": "故法令不急而行，民不勞而上足用，故民歸之。", "canonical_ref": "6.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "當今之主，其爲舟車與此異矣。", "text_normalized": "當今之主，其爲舟車與此異矣。", "canonical_ref": "6.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "全固輕利皆已具，必厚作斂於百姓，以飾舟車，飾車以文采，飾舟以刻鏤。", "text_normalized": "全固輕利皆已具，必厚作斂於百姓，以飾舟車，飾車以文采，飾舟以刻鏤。", "canonical_ref": "6.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "女子廢其紡織而修文采，故民寒；", "text_normalized": "女子廢其紡織而修文采，故民寒；", "canonical_ref": "6.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "男子離其耕稼而修刻鏤，故民饑。", "text_normalized": "男子離其耕稼而修刻鏤，故民饑。", "canonical_ref": "6.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "人君爲舟車若此，故左右象之。", "text_normalized": "人君爲舟車若此，故左右象之。", "canonical_ref": "6.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "是以其民饑寒並至，故爲姦邪。", "text_normalized": "是以其民饑寒並至，故爲姦邪。", "canonical_ref": "6.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "奸邪多則刑罰深，刑罰深則國亂。", "text_normalized": "奸邪多則刑罰深，刑罰深則國亂。", "canonical_ref": "6.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂，當爲舟車不可不節。", "text_normalized": "君實欲天下之治而惡其亂，當爲舟車不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "凡回於天地之間，包於四海之內，天壤之情，陰陽之和，莫不有也，雖至聖不能更也。", "text_normalized": "凡回於天地之間，包於四海之內，天壤之情，陰陽之和，莫不有也，雖至聖不能更也。", "canonical_ref": "6.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "何以知其然？", "text_normalized": "何以知其然？", "canonical_ref": "6.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "聖人有傳：", "text_normalized": "聖人有傳：", "canonical_ref": "6.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "天地也，則曰上下；", "text_normalized": "天地也，則曰上下；", "canonical_ref": "6.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "四時也，則曰陰陽；", "text_normalized": "四時也，則曰陰陽；", "canonical_ref": "6.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "人情也，則曰男女；", "text_normalized": "人情也，則曰男女；", "canonical_ref": "6.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "禽獸也，則曰牡牝、雄雌也。", "text_normalized": "禽獸也，則曰牡牝、雄雌也。", "canonical_ref": "6.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "真天壤之情，雖有先王不能更也。", "text_normalized": "真天壤之情，雖有先王不能更也。", "canonical_ref": "6.73", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 74, "text_original": "雖上世至聖必蓄私，不以傷行，故民無怨。", "text_normalized": "雖上世至聖必蓄私，不以傷行，故民無怨。", "canonical_ref": "6.74", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "宮無拘女，故天下無寡夫。", "text_normalized": "宮無拘女，故天下無寡夫。", "canonical_ref": "6.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "內無拘女，外無寡夫，故天下之民衆。", "text_normalized": "內無拘女，外無寡夫，故天下之民衆。", "canonical_ref": "6.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "當今之君，其蓄私也，大國拘女累千，小國累百，是以天下之男多寡無妻，女多拘無夫，男女失時，故民少。", "text_normalized": "當今之君，其蓄私也，大國拘女累千，小國累百，是以天下之男多寡無妻，女多拘無夫，男女失時，故民少。", "canonical_ref": "6.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "君實欲民之衆而惡其寡，當蓄私不可不節。", "text_normalized": "君實欲民之衆而惡其寡，當蓄私不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.78", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 79, "text_original": "凡此五者，聖人之所儉節也，小人之所淫佚也。", "text_normalized": "凡此五者，聖人之所儉節也，小人之所淫佚也。", "canonical_ref": "6.79", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "儉節則昌，淫佚則亡，此五者不可不節。", "text_normalized": "儉節則昌，淫佚則亡，此五者不可不節。", "canonical_ref": "6.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess", "source_id": "mozi-006-indulgence-in-excess__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "夫婦節而天地和，風雨節而五穀孰，衣服節而肌膚和。", "text_normalized": "夫婦節而天地和，風雨節而五穀孰，衣服節而肌膚和。", "canonical_ref": "6.81", "notes": ""}
